    "This performance indicates that the proposed model accounts for almost all the changes in the enrolment data suggesting its predicting strength.",
    "In every aspect, in this instance all other models were inferior to the model, as the model recorded the highest R2 coupled with the best MSE, MSRE, NMSE, RMSE and MAPE distinctively the lowest returns.",
